          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". A long running rhythm game series mainly featured in Japan, but has had a few console releases in English. Brought to us by Bandai Namco, it has a colourful, joyous and cutesy aesthetic with an extremely impressive track list that includes over 500 songs (and growing). Grab your drumsticks, and DON your way to becoming a Taiko Master!",
