            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " main theme can be found here too. Not to mention a selection of Vocaloid songs. As you can see, from this SMALL selection I’ve provided, there is a HUGE variety of songs to choose from.",
